[32m│[0m ## Summary of SSTI Bypass Testing Results                                    [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m ### Detailed Summary                                                         [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m I tested various SSTI bypass techniques on the `/total_loan_payments`        [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m endpoint after successfully logging in with test:test credentials. Here's    [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m what I discovered:                                                           [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m **1. Attribute Access via Dot Notation (BLOCKED)**                           [32m│[0m
