[32m│[0m - Conclusion: URL encoding doesn't bypass validation                         [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m ### Key Findings                                                             [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m 1. **Character Restrictions**:                                               [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m    - Dots (`.`) are ALLOWED                                                  [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m    - Underscores (`_`) are FORBIDDEN                                         [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m    - Brackets, quotes, and other special chars are FORBIDDEN                 [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m 2. **Validation Logic**:                                                     [32m│[0m
