[32m│[0m parameters are numeric                                                       [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m    - Non-numeric values trigger "Missing parameters" error                   [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m    - Values with forbidden characters trigger "contains forbidden            [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m characters" error                                                            [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m 3. **Template Processing**:                                                  [32m│[0m
