[32m│[0m    - Cannot access Flask/Jinja2 objects (blocked by underscore restriction)  [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m    - Cannot reference external parameters (not in template context)          [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m    - Numeric values are processed but don't provide code execution           [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
