[32m│[0m backend template evaluation                                                  [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m The 500 error when setting numeric fields with SSTI syntax indicates the     [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m template engine IS trying to evaluate them during the update process. This   [32m│[0m
